#: includes/class-wc-privacy.php:121
msgid ""
"In this section you should list who you’re sharing data with, and for what "
"purpose. This could include, but may not be limited to, analytics, marketing,"
" payment gateways, shipping providers, and third party embeds."
msgstr ""
"U ovom odeljku treba da navedete sa kim delite podatke i u koju svrhu. To "
"može da obuhvati, bez ograničenja, pružaoce usluga analitike, marketinga, "
"špedicije, posrednike u platnom prometu, kao i ugnježdene servise trećih "
"strana."

#: includes/class-wc-privacy.php:126
msgid ""
"In this subsection you should list which third party payment processors "
"you’re using to take payments on your store since these may handle customer "
"data. We’ve included PayPal as an example, but you should remove this if "
"you’re not using PayPal."
msgstr ""
"U ovom delu treba da navedete treća lica koja vrše obračun platnog prometa, "
"a čije usluge koristite za plaćanje u vašoj prodavnici, pošto ta lica mogu "
"da rukuju podacima o kupcu. PayPal smo stavili za primer, a vi treba da "
"uklonite PayPal ako ga ne koristite."

