#: assets/client/blocks/product-reviews.js:1
msgid ""
"The <aside> element should represent a portion of a document whose content "
"is only indirectly related to the document's main content."
msgstr ""
"<aside> element treba da predstavlja deo dokumenta čiji je sadržaj samo "
"indirektno povezan sa glavnim sadržajem dokumenta."

#: assets/client/blocks/product-reviews.js:1
msgid ""
"The <div> element should only be used if the block is a design element with "
"no semantic meaning."
msgstr ""
"<div> element treba koristiti samo ako je blok dizajnerski element bez "
"semantičkog značenja."

#: assets/client/blocks/product-reviews.js:1
msgid ""
"The <footer> element should represent a footer for its nearest sectioning "
"element (e.g.: <section>, <article>, <main> etc.)."
msgstr ""
"<footer> element treba da predstavlja podnožje za svoj najbliži element za "
"sekcionisanje (npr. <section>, <article>, <main> itd.)."

#: assets/client/blocks/product-reviews.js:1
msgid ""
"The <header> element should represent introductory content, typically a "
"group of introductory or navigational aids."
msgstr ""
"<header> element treba da predstavlja uvodni sadržaj, obično grupu uvodnih "
"ili navigacionih pomagala."

#: assets/client/blocks/product-reviews.js:1
msgid ""
"The <main> element should be used for the primary content of your document "
"only."
msgstr ""
"<main> element treba koristiti samo za primarni sadržaj vašeg dokumenta."

#: assets/client/blocks/product-reviews.js:1
msgid ""
"The <nav> element should be used to identify groups of links that are "
"intended to be used for website or page content navigation."
msgstr ""
"<nav> element treba koristiti za identifikaciju grupa linkova namenjenih za "
"navigaciju po veb sajtu ili sadržaju stranice."

#: assets/client/blocks/product-reviews.js:1
msgid ""
"The <section> element should represent a standalone portion of the document "
"that can't be better represented by another element."
msgstr ""
"<section> element treba da predstavlja samostalni deo dokumenta koji se ne "
"može bolje predstaviti drugim elementom."

