#, js-format
msgid ""
"This block lists reviews for a selected product. %s doesn't have any reviews "
"yet, but they will show up here when it does."
msgstr ""
"Ovaj blok prikazuje preglede za izabrani proizvod. %s još uvek nema "
"recenzija, ali one će se pojaviti ovde čim ih bude."

