msgid ""
"This block shows a list of all product reviews. Your store does not have any "
"reviews yet, but they will show up here when it does."
msgstr ""
"Ovaj blok prikazuje listu svih pregleda proizvoda. Vaša prodavnica još uvek "
"nema recenzija, ali one će se pojaviti ovde kada ih bude."

