"uključujući trenutne korpe i korpe sačuvane u bazi podataka."

#: includes/rest-api/Controllers/Version2/class-wc-rest-system-status-tools-v2-controller.php:142
msgid "This tool will delete all variations which have no parent."
msgstr ""
"Ovaj alat će obrisati sve varijacije za koje ne postoji matični proizvod."

#: includes/rest-api/Controllers/Version2/class-wc-rest-system-status-tools-v2-controller.php:147
msgid ""
"This tool will delete expired download permissions and permissions with 0 "
"remaining downloads."
msgstr ""
"Ovaj alat će obrisati istekla ovlašćenja za preuzimanje i ovlašćenja sa 0 "
"preostalih preuzimanja."

#: includes/rest-api/Controllers/Version2/class-wc-rest-system-status-tools-v2-controller.php:193
