#: includes/rest-api/Controllers/Version2/class-wc-rest-system-status-tools-v2-controller.php:225
msgid ""
"This tool will update your WooCommerce database to the latest version. "
"Please ensure you make sufficient backups before proceeding."
msgstr ""
"Ovaj alat ažurira vašu WooCommerce bazu podataka na poslednju verziju. "
"Obavezno napravite kopiju baze podataka pre nego što nastavite."

